": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 142462, "create_time": 1653367258, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 评价机制是由老师给出的，不如直接找老师商讨。学校那么多课，总不会有人一门一门地看看评价机制是否合理，所以最后还是落实到任课老师身上", "timestamp": 1653367258}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 142475, "create_time": 1653367436, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Francis: 任课老师（实验课组长）明确表示需要由学校决定", "timestamp": 1653367436}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 142491, "create_time": 1653367744, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 哈哈，甩锅大赛，看来任课教师、学校都不愿意替你承担风险，你可能只能靠自己了", "timestamp": 1653367744}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 142500, "create_time": 1653367822, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 7, "text": "中肯的，有些话不能说太明白", "timestamp": 1653367822}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 142646, "create_time": 1653370641, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Dave: 那就是不会改了\n互相甩锅xs", "timestamp": 1653370641}], "create_time": 1653363329, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1653370641, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 20, "pid": 48432, "poll": null, "reply": 20, "text": "润不润，其实是个人的选择，指望学校“出正式通知”是不可能的。比如出国留学，学校允许，会提供各种支持，你可以看到一些通知说“如果你要出国，你需要办某某手续”，但你不可能看到一份通知写“学校鼓励大家出国留学”。目前返乡基本上是同理，学校可以说“想返乡的同学可以按某某方式申请”，但不可能说“鼓励大家返乡”。", "timestamp": 1653363329}}